      <title>线性表的应用</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/23/xian-xing-biao-de-ying-yong/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/23/xian-xing-biao-de-ying-yong/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1）合并有序线性表"><a href="#1）合并有序线性表" class="headerlink" title="1）合并有序线性表"></a>1）合并有序线性表</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;typedef int DataType;#include&lt;list.h&gt;#define ListSize 200void MergeList(SeqList A, SeqList B, SeqList* pC);int main()&#123;int i;int a[] &#x3D; &#123; 1,6,10,10,15 &#125;;int b[] &#x3D; &#123; 2,3,13,16,18 &#125;;DataType e;SeqList A, B, C;InitList(&amp;A);InitList(&amp;B);InitList(&amp;C);&#x2F;&#x2F;1)将数组a放进线性表A中for (i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; sizeof(a) &#x2F; sizeof(a[0]); i++)&#x2F;&#x2F;要知道数组长度&#123;if (InsertList(&amp;A, i, a[i - 1]) !&#x3D; 1)&#x2F;&#x2F;插入元素&#123;printf(&quot;插入A时位置不合法\n&quot;);return;&#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F;2)将数组b放进线性表B中for (i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; sizeof(b) &#x2F; sizeof(b[0]); i++)&#123;if (InsertList(&amp;B, i, b[i - 1]) !&#x3D; 1)&#123;printf(&quot;插入B时位置不合法\n&quot;);return;&#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F;3）输出线性表A的元素printf(&quot;A中元素为：\n&quot;);for (i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; A.length; i++)&#123;if (GetElem(&amp;A, i, &amp;e) &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)printf(&quot;%4d&quot;, e);&#125;printf(&quot;\n&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;4）输出线性表B的元素printf(&quot;B中元素为：\n&quot;);for (i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; B.length; i++)&#123;if (GetElem(&amp;B, i, &amp;e) &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)printf(&quot;%4d&quot;, e);&#125;printf(&quot;\n&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;5）调用MergeList()函数MergeList(A, B, &amp;C);&#x2F;&#x2F;6）输出线性表Cprintf(&quot;C中元素为：\n&quot;);for (i &#x3D; 1; i &lt;&#x3D; C.length; i++)&#123;GetElem(&amp;C, i, &amp;e);printf(&quot;%4d&quot;, e);&#125;printf(&quot;\n&quot;);return 0;&#125;void MergeList(SeqList A, SeqList B, SeqList* pC)&#123;int a &#x3D; 1, b &#x3D; 1, c &#x3D; 1;DataType e1, e2;while (a &lt;&#x3D; A.length &amp;&amp; b &lt;&#x3D; B.length)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;从A，B中分别获取e1,e2GetElem(&amp;A, a, &amp;e1);GetElem(&amp;B, b, &amp;e2);&#x2F;&#x2F;比较e1,e2,并将e1(e2)放进C中，A(B)下标+1，C下标+1if (e1 &lt;&#x3D; e2)&#123;InsertList(pC, c, e1);a++;c++;&#125;else&#123;InsertList(pC, c, e2);b++;c++;&#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F;若A(B)未完则将A中剩余元素放入Cwhile (a &lt;&#x3D; A.length)&#123;GetElem(&amp;A, a, &amp;e1);InsertList(pC, c, e1);a++;c++;&#125;while (b &lt;&#x3D; B.length)&#123;GetElem(&amp;B, b, &amp;e2);InsertList(pC, c, e2);b++;c++;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F;设置C的长度pC-&gt;length &#x3D; A.length + B.length;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
