      <title>C预处理器和C库</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/21/c-yu-chu-li-qi-he-c-ku/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/21/c-yu-chu-li-qi-he-c-ku/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、明示常量：-define"><a href="#一、明示常量：-define" class="headerlink" title="一、明示常量：#define"></a>一、明示常量：#define</h1><p>用于记号替换</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#define A red&#x2F;&#x2F;在预处理时所有A都被替换为red#define F(X) X*X&#x2F;&#x2F;与函数类似#define G printf(&quot;abc&quot;)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="1）运算符"><a href="#1）运算符" class="headerlink" title="1）运算符"></a>1）运算符</h2><p>1.用宏参数创建字符串：#运算符</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#define F(A,B) printf(&quot;A + B &#x3D; %d&quot;,A + B)F(2,1);&#x2F;&#x2F;输出：A + B &#x3D; 3#define F(A,B) printf(&quot;&quot;#A&quot; + &quot;#B&quot; &#x3D; %d&quot;,A + B)F(2,1);&#x2F;&#x2F;输出：2 + 1 &#x3D; 3<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="2）预处理器粘合剂：-运算符"><a href="#2）预处理器粘合剂：-运算符" class="headerlink" title="2）预处理器粘合剂：##运算符"></a>2）预处理器粘合剂：##运算符</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#define XNAME(n) x ## nXNAME(4)  &#x2F;&#x2F;即x4<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="3）变参宏：…和-VA-ARGS"><a href="#3）变参宏：…和-VA-ARGS" class="headerlink" title="3）变参宏：…和__VA_ARGS__"></a>3）变参宏：…和__VA_ARGS__</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#define PR(...) printf(__VA_ARGS__)PR(&quot;hollow&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;输出：hollow<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>Tip：省略号只能用于最后的宏参数。</p></blockquote><h1 id="二、文件包含：-include"><a href="#二、文件包含：-include" class="headerlink" title="二、文件包含：#include"></a>二、文件包含：#include</h1><h1 id="三、其它指令"><a href="#三、其它指令" class="headerlink" title="三、其它指令"></a>三、其它指令</h1><ol><li>#ifdef </li><li>#else</li><li>#endif</li><li>#ifndef</li><li>#if    ——后跟整型常量表达式</li><li>#elif</li><li>#line——重置__LINE__和__FILE__</li><li>#error——让预处理器发出一条报错消息</li><li>#pragma</li><li>_Pragma运算符——解字符串，即把字符串中的转义序列转换成对应字符</li><li>_Generic预算符——泛型选择表达式</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
