        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1）整数转二进制打印"><a href="#1）整数转二进制打印" class="headerlink" title="1）整数转二进制打印"></a>1）整数转二进制打印</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt; static int b &#x3D; 0;unsigned long f(int a);int main()&#123;    int a &#x3D; 73;    printf(&quot;%d&quot;, f(a));    return 0;&#125;unsigned long f(int a)&#123;    b &#x3D; b * 10 + a % 2;    if (a &#x3D;&#x3D; 1)        return b;    else        return f(a &#x2F; 2);&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="2-二进制转整数"><a href="#2-二进制转整数" class="headerlink" title="2)二进制转整数"></a>2)二进制转整数</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;int f(char* pbin, int length);int main()&#123;char* pbin &#x3D; &quot;01001001&quot;;int a &#x3D; f(pbin, sizeof(pbin));printf(&quot;%d&quot;, a);return 0;&#125;int f(char* pbin, int length)&#123;int n &#x3D; 0;for (int i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; length; i++)&#123;n &#x3D; n * 2 + (pbin[i] - &#39;0&#39;);&#x2F;&#x2F;&#39;1&#39;的ASCII码为49，&#39;0&#39;的ASCII码为48&#125;return n;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
