      <title>结构和其他数据形式</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/14/jie-gou-he-qi-ta-shu-ju-xing-shi/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/14/jie-gou-he-qi-ta-shu-ju-xing-shi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1）建立结构声明"><a href="#1）建立结构声明" class="headerlink" title="1）建立结构声明"></a>1）建立结构声明</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct book &#123;    char title[30];    char author[10];    float value;&#125;;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>结构声明的每个部分称为成员(或字段)，成员可以是任意一种C的数据类型或其它结构</p><h2 id="2）定义结构变量"><a href="#2）定义结构变量" class="headerlink" title="2）定义结构变量"></a>2）定义结构变量</h2><ul><li>先声明结构，再定义变量，可定义多个变量<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct book &#123;    char title[30];    char author[10];    float value;&#125;;struct book library;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li>同时声明结构和定义变量，只能定义一个变量<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct &#123;            &#x2F;&#x2F;无结构标记    char title[30];    char author[10];    float value;&#125; library;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="3）初始化结构"><a href="#3）初始化结构" class="headerlink" title="3）初始化结构"></a>3）初始化结构</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct book &#123;    char title[30];    char author[10];    float value;&#125;;struct book library &#x3D; &#123;    &quot;The book name&quot;,        &#x2F;&#x2F;用逗号隔开    &quot;author name&quot;,    20&#125;;struct book library &#x3D; &#123;    .value &#x3D; 20;            &#x2F;&#x2F;只初始化value&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="4）访问结构成员"><a href="#4）访问结构成员" class="headerlink" title="4）访问结构成员"></a>4）访问结构成员</h2>使用结构成员运算符”.”<h2 id="5）结构与成员的赋值"><a href="#5）结构与成员的赋值" class="headerlink" title="5）结构与成员的赋值"></a>5）结构与成员的赋值</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct book library, shop;library &#x3D; shop;         &#x2F;&#x2F;结构变量 &#x3D; 结构变量library &#x3D; &#123;    &quot;name&quot;,    &quot;author name&quot;,    15&#125;library.title &#x3D; &quot;name&quot;library &#x3D; (struct book) &#123;         &#x2F;&#x2F;复合字面量    &quot;name&quot;,    &quot;author&quot;,    15&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="6）指向结构的指针"><a href="#6）指向结构的指针" class="headerlink" title="6）指向结构的指针"></a>6）指向结构的指针</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">struct fellow &#123;    int number;&#125;;struct book &#123;    char title[30];    char author[10];    float value;    struct fellow page; &#125;;struct book a;struct book str[10];    &#x2F;&#x2F;结构数组，含有10个结构变量struct book* ps,*ps2; ps &#x3D; &amp;a;            &#x2F;&#x2F;结构变量名不会自动转换为地址，必须有&amp;ps2 &#x3D; &amp;s[0] &#x3D;&#x3D; &amp;(s[0])        &#x2F;&#x2F;ps2指向结构数组的第一个结构变量ps-&gt;title[0] &#x3D;&#x3D; a.title[0] &#x3D;&#x3D; (*ps).title[0]    &#x2F;&#x2F;访问成员<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="7）复合字面量"><a href="#7）复合字面量" class="headerlink" title="7）复合字面量"></a>7）复合字面量</h2>适用于数组和结构，用于赋值或函数参数<blockquote><p>Tip：1.用数组复合字面量做函数参数时，该数组传递的不是地址，而是整个数组  </p></blockquote></li></ul><p>2.结构变量不会自动转换成地址</p>]]></content>
      
      
